  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个8通道的DMA调度系统，核心是Scheduler Group Array。每个通道有独立的APB接口，比如APB CH0到APB CH7，这些需要连接到各自的调度组。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB0",
        "APB1",
        "APB7",
        "GRP0",
        "GRP1",
        "GRP7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以APB CH0对应GRP0，APB CH1对应GRP1，以此类推。这些调度组内部需要配置DESC ID和SCHED ID对吧？比如CH0是DESC ID=16，SCHED ID=48？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB0",
        "GRP0",
        "APB1",
        "GRP1",
        "APB7",
        "GRP7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，CH0是16和48，CH1是17和49，CH7是23和55。另外还需要一个Global Config模块，统一配置所有调度组。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "GRP0",
        "GRP1",
        "GRP7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把CFG画出来，连接到三个GRP节点。现在来看调度组内部的数据流，描述符请求怎么走？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CFG",
        "GRP0",
        "GRP1",
        "GRP7"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "每个GRP通过desc_ar_*信号汇聚到一个8通道轮询仲裁器，叫Descriptor AR Arbiter。所有GRP0、GRP1到GRP7都连到这个AR_ARB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GRP0",
        "GRP1",
        "GRP7",
        "AR_ARB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，AR_ARB在子图中央。接下来仲裁器输出到哪儿？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR_ARB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "AR_ARB通过desc_axi_ar_*连接到Shared Descriptor AXI Master，也就是DESC_AXI。这是共享的描述符AXI主设备。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AR_ARB",
        "DESC_AXI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "DESC_AXI的读返回数据怎么分发回各个通道？需要广播吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_AXI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，DESC_AXI通过desc_axi_r_*连到R Broadcast模块，R_BCAST根据ID把描述符读返回数据claim到对应的GRP。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DESC_AXI",
        "R_BCAST",
        "GRP0",
        "GRP1",
        "GRP7"
